title: Oru Nalla Naal Paathu Solren
subTitle: Yaman, a tribal leader, arrives in Chennai to kidnap the woman whom he has sworn to marry. However, the woman's classmates pose as an obstacle in his plans.

title: Pesadha Kannum Pesume
subTitle: Vikram, a habitual prankster, decides to play a prank on his lover, Swetha, by telling her he is already married. However, his plan backfires on him when Swetha's marriage gets fixed with another man.

title: Piragu
subTitle: Sathya, an aspiring film director, moves to Chennai to pursue his dream. However, his life takes a complicated turn when he is targeted by two rival gangs.

title: Teleshopping
subTitle: Learn about a wide selection of products and take advantage of a convenient method of shopping. A show for those who love to shop from the comforts of their home.

title: King
subTitle: Raja and his father, who live in Hong Kong, are devastated when an accident leaves the latter on the verge of death. He decides to reunite his father with his grandfather in order to make him happy.

title: Naiyaandi
subTitle: Chinna and Vanaroja are in love, but in an unexpected turn of events, her marriage is fixed with someone else. Vanaroja escapes and comes to live with Chinna's family, but his brothers fall for her.

title: Ayan
subTitle: Deva, a computer science student, works with a smuggler against his mother's wishes. His life unravels when his closest friend is murdered, leading him to help the police catch a powerful drug lord.

title: Maaveeran
subTitle: Harsha gets falsely implicated for killing Indu's father. However, he soon realises that he and Indu share a bond from a previous life and sets out to set things straight.

title: Gulebagavali
subTitle: A businessperson sends three thieves to find hidden treasure in a village named Gulaebaghavali. A fourth criminal joins the gang midway, and they plan to divide the loot among themselves.

title: Raam
subTitle: Ram, a young man who is extremely attached to his mother, is suspected to be behind her murder. Soon, the combined efforts of Ram and the police lead them to the real killer.

title: Ponnu Oorukku Pudhusu
subTitle: Rukmani faces challenges when she moves to a new town. When a man named Pichaimuthu loves her, she gets torn between his love and her career.

title: Pokkiri Thambi
subTitle: In a village where women mysteriously disappear and end up dead, an unfortunate incident reveals a shocking truth about the village's head.

title: Teleshopping

title: Ponmanam
subTitle: An unemployed Anandhan's family has no expectations from him. However, when his parents commit suicide after his sister elopes, he is determined to find her.

title: Ivargal Indiyargal
subTitle: Savithiri resides with Periyanayagi, a woman known for her unwavering adherence to rules. Despite this environment, Savithiri becomes enamored with Ramu, who comes from humble circumstances.

title: Thoongathey Thambi Thoongathey
subTitle: Gopi, an unemployed graduate, falls in love with Padmini, the daughter of a rich businessman. Padmini finds Vinod, Gopi's lookalike, who turns out to be his brother.

title: Asathal
subTitle: Vetri and his two best friends live together and follow a carefree lifestyle. However, things become complicated when they encounter an abandoned baby at their doorstep.

title: Sketch
subTitle: Sketch works under a loan shark who takes the vehicles of those who are unable to pay him back. However, one such defaulter is a deadly gangster who turns livid when he finds that his car is taken.

title: Thaikulame Thaikulame
subTitle: A man enters a bizarre circumstance that requires him to marry again. However, news about his second marriage reaches his first wife.

title: Thaikulame Thaikulame

title: Pirappu
subTitle: Padma's father pushes for her engagement to Kannan despite his dislike for him. However, things spiral out of control when Kannan refuses, as he is in love with another woman.

title: Poo Pootha Nandha Vanam
subTitle: After losing her unborn child, Shakuntala learns that she can never be intimate with her husband. She tries to get her husband remarried to her sister, but he disapproves of her plan.

title: Sigappu Rojakkal
subTitle: A young man, traumatised by his past, grows up to despise the opposite sex and exploits them. However, things take a turn when he falls in love with a woman prisoner while in jail.

title: Bala
subTitle: Bala, a hitman, falls for the daughter of the rival gang's leader, but his love is threatened when the two gangs decide to forge family ties.

title: Makkal Aanaiyittal
subTitle: Kadhiravan and his friend, Mohan, fight against the atrocities of a corrupt politician. Mohan gets killed and Kadhiravan plots revenge against the politician and his men.

title: Naayak
subTitle: Siddharth and Charan, two lookalikes who are fighting their own battles against evildoers, cross paths and join forces to take down Rawat, a ruthless minister.

title: Marutha
subTitle: Unable to return her brother's monetary favour, Meenakshi's husband ends his life. When her brother's wife expects her to repay the money, Meenakshi sees it as a chance to reclaim her lost honour.

title: Vasanthi
subTitle: Released from prison after committing a crime, a young man learns about his orphaned sister. Soon, he turns to a life of crime to support her.
